<HEADLINE>
FT  06 OCT 94 / World News in Brief: Austrian emergency
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Austria was on nationwide alert for letterbombs after a judge presiding over
a neo-Nazi trial in Vienna warned that a new campaign could be under way in
the run-up to a general election on Sunday.
