investment'.
Molson Breweries, the brewing unit, is expected to take a stake in a joint
venture established earlier this year by Foster's of Australia and the Hong
Kong conglomerate Wheelock to set up breweries in China, where beer demand
is growing at 20 per cent annually.
Molson Breweries is 40 per cent owned by Molson, 40 per cent by Foster's and
